OL,3,C'At a tipping point': Calls for urgent
OL,4,Cinvestment into cancer research
OL,6,FTwo women from are calling for urgent
OL,7,Finvestments in cancer research after
OL,8,Fdiscovering they share the same faulty
OL,9,Fgene.
OL,11,FMutations in the BRCA gene
OL,12,Fdramatically increase the chance of
OL,13,Fpeople developing breast, ovarian and
OL,14,Fpancreatic cancers - up to 90% in some
OL,15,Fcases.
OL,17,FIt is estimated that one in every 400
OL,18,Fpeople has the faulty gene, meaning
OL,19,Fcells can grow uncontrollably.
