OL,3,C'At a tipping point': Calls for urgent
OL,4,Cinvestment into cancer research
OL,6,FDani Barnett had a double mastectomy
OL,7,Fand her ovaries were removed to lower
OL,8,Fher risk after discovering she has the
OL,9,Ffaulty gene.
OL,11,FShe says: "I had an 80% chance of
OL,12,Fdeveloping breast cancer which is
OL,13,Fincredibly scary at 28 and through
OL,14,Fresearch they showed that if you had a
OL,15,Fdouble mastectomy, that lowered your
OL,16,Fchances to 3%.
