OL,6,F"To put it into perspective, your
OL,7,Faverage woman has a 13% chance so I
OL,8,Fwould be better than your average
OL,9,Fhuman after having the double
OL,10,Fmastectomy."
OL,12,FVikki Hammond also has the faulty gene
OL,13,Fand was diagnosed with breast cancer
OL,14,Fin August 2021.
