OL,3,C'At a tipping point': Calls for urgent
OL,4,Cinvestment into cancer research
OL,6,FShe explains her journey: "Mine
OL,7,Fstarted 30 years ago when a relative
OL,8,Fof mine got diagnosed with breast
OL,9,Fcancer. She got picked up by the
OL,10,Fcancer research team in Southampton
OL,11,Fand that's when they started looking
OL,12,Fat how genetics have an impact on
OL,13,Fcancer, so as a family we got tested.
OL,15,F"If it wasn't for her and us getting
OL,16,Ftested I wouldn't know we were
OL,17,Fcarriers."
