OL,3,C'At a tipping point': Calls for urgent
OL,4,Cinvestment into cancer research
OL,6,FProfessor Gareth Griffiths, Director
OL,7,Fof Southampton's Clinical Trial Unit
OL,8,Fwhich Cancer Research UK funds, joined
OL,9,Fother leading scientists to write an
OL,10,Fopen letter stating the world is at a
OL,11,F"tipping point".
OL,13,FHe explains: "We're standing on the
OL,14,Fbrink of discoveries like new blood
OL,15,Ftests that could detect cancer at an
OL,16,Fearlier stage, and algorithms that
OL,17,Fcould predict someone's cancer risk
OL,18,Fand stop it from developing in the
OL,19,Ffirst place.
