OL,3,C'At a tipping point': Calls for urgent
OL,4,Cinvestment into cancer research
OL,6,F"What we want to move from is the
OL,7,Fsituation that individuals get early
OL,8,Fcancer but have no symptoms and the
OL,9,Ffirst time they come to the hospital
OL,10,Fis when they get certain symptoms.
OL,12,F"They could be physical like blood or
OL,13,Fpain and at that point, we're finding
OL,14,Fout the cancer is quite advanced and
OL,15,Fspread throughout the body as the
OL,16,Fcancer is a lot harder to treat at
OL,17,Fthat stage."
